        Transforms that just need to iterate over each concept in the DB may implement this interface - this transform method will be called once for each concept in the DB. Transformations should be limited to operations that involve this concept.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
        ts - - the term store
        cc - - the current concept
        Returns:
